sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as You
    participant CC as Claude Code
    participant WB as .claude/workbooks/
    participant EX as Explore agent
    participant PL as Plan agent
    participant SP as Specialist agent
    participant GE as Gemini MCP
    participant FS as Project files
    participant ARC as ~/claude-archive

    U->>CC: "Implement feature X across modules"
    CC->>WB: open YYYY-MM-DD-feature-x.md
    Note over CC,WB: Workbook = episodic memory<br/>across all turns of this mission

    par parallel recon
        CC->>EX: "Find existing patterns for X"
    and
        CC->>EX: "Find tests covering X-adjacent code"
    end
    EX-->>CC: file paths + line citations

    CC->>PL: "Design implementation given recon"
    PL-->>CC: written plan w/ verification gates

    CC-->>U: ExitPlanMode (approval requested)
    U-->>CC: approves

    loop per plan step
        CC->>SP: dispatch specialist
        SP->>FS: edits files
        SP-->>CC: handover block (file:line evidence)
        CC->>WB: append handover
    end

    opt adversarial check
        CC->>GE: gemini_second_opinion(plan, draft)
        GE-->>CC: red-team feedback
    end

    CC->>FS: run tests / verifier
    FS-->>CC: PASS: 38 / REGRESSIONS: 0

    CC->>WB: write Final synthesis, Status: closed
    U->>CC: /exit

    CC->>ARC: Stop hook archives transcript + WB + plans
    Note over ARC: Now grep-able forever
